# ✍️ AI Writing Assistant

An AI-powered writing assistant built with the **MERN stack**, designed to help users improve their writing through **grammar check, spell check, and rephrasing**.  

This project uses **Cohere APIs** for natural language processing and **Privy** for authentication (login/signup).  

---

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ User authentication with **Privy** (Login / Signup).  
- ✅ AI-powered **Grammar Check**.  
- ✅ AI-powered **Spell Check**.  
- ✅ AI-powered **Rephrase / Rewrite sentences**.  
- ✅ Clean UI with **React + Tailwind CSS**.  
- ✅ Fast development setup using **Vite**.  
- ✅ Backend API built with **Express** and **MongoDB**.  

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

**Frontend:**  
- React  
- Tailwind CSS  
- Vite  

**Backend:**  
- Node.js  
- Express  
- MongoDB  

**AI & Authentication:**  
- Cohere API (Grammar, Spell Check, Rephrase)  
- Privy (Authentication)  

---

